{
  "texts": [
    "Research by Chiu [2] suggests that future higher education should be transformed in order that students and educators are trained in learning and teaching with generative AI, and develop and enhance AI literacy skills.",
    "Limitations and future researchRegarding the limitations of this study, initially, the queries submitted to ChatGPT did not identify the specific context of AI in terms of, for example, education mode (face-to-face, online, blended mode) or discipline (field of study).",
    "Since the pandemic accelerated the digitalization of higher education, and blended/online education is on the rise [70], it is suggested to investigate AI affordances within different education modes.",
    "For instance, Dogan et al. [71] reviewed AI affordances and uses in online education environments.",
    "It is also suggested to explore AI's affordances, possibilities, and limitations within specific academic subjects."
  ]
}